WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.731 --> 00:00:01.966
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.966 --> 00:00:04.091
How are you doing today?

00:00:04.537 --> 00:00:05.873
Praise the Lord.

00:00:05.873 --> 00:00:09.000
We are going to do some things in the spirit realm today.

00:00:09.253 --> 00:00:10.949
We're going to take some territory.

00:00:10.949 --> 00:00:18.240
We're not going to allow the devil to come in and rob us of the House of Representatives.

00:00:19.234 --> 00:00:23.340
You can obviously see what they're trying to do.

00:00:23.640 --> 00:00:36.400
I told you all to pray over Nevada and Arizona already and the metal buildings and all the things that I warned you about already by the Spirit of God and what the Lord showed me they were going to try to do.

00:00:36.740 --> 00:00:42.040
Now they're trying to delay it all the time, trying to say, 'Oh, well, you know, we have to have more time.

00:00:42.040 --> 00:00:43.600
' Folks, it's corruption.

00:00:43.600 --> 00:00:45.156
You know it, and I know it.

00:00:46.187 --> 00:00:50.630
So, we're going to take authority.

00:00:50.640 --> 00:00:53.351
Thank you to all the people praying for me about the cough.

00:00:53.351 --> 00:01:00.160
I got these Thieves cough drops, and I'm telling you they are really helping.

00:01:00.160 --> 00:01:03.893
I give God glory for the things He put in this earth to help us.

00:01:04.720 --> 00:01:06.434
Those Thieves are really helping me.

00:01:06.434 --> 00:01:09.028
My wife got those for me, and I'm very thankful.

00:01:09.028 --> 00:01:15.063
To all the people who have been praying and giving me remedies and everything, thank you for your compassion and your love for us.

00:01:15.063 --> 00:01:16.560
It really blesses me.

00:01:18.914 --> 00:01:21.573
My wife tells me every day, 'You've had a lot of people today.

00:01:21.573 --> 00:01:28.159
' Yesterday, probably a hundred people or so reached out to give me something for the cough.

00:01:29.119 --> 00:01:32.640
It's just a virus and it has no right to stay in my body.

00:01:32.889 --> 00:01:35.573
I'm healed by His stripes and I come against it.

00:01:35.804 --> 00:01:38.810
I just want you all to know we appreciate you.

00:01:38.810 --> 00:01:41.291
There are a lot of loving people.

00:01:42.662 --> 00:01:52.479
We're going to take communion and we're going to believe God together today for a supernatural turnaround in the House of Representatives that this stops now.

00:01:52.479 --> 00:01:53.759
That the corruption stops.

00:01:53.759 --> 00:01:56.640
We're going to believe God for our healings today.

00:01:56.640 --> 00:02:02.740
I believe with all my heart that Jesus Christ is the healer.

00:02:02.740 --> 00:02:06.799
I have it upside down; I put a sweatshirt on here.

00:02:06.799 --> 00:02:08.068
Jesus the Healer.

00:02:08.068 --> 00:02:10.539
That's what we believe in this household.

00:02:10.539 --> 00:02:14.550
I hope you believe it for your household because He is a healer.

00:02:14.550 --> 00:02:16.430
He is the healer.

00:02:16.430 --> 00:02:21.165
He's the same yesterday, today, and forever, ladies and gentlemen.

00:02:21.508 --> 00:02:25.467
He is healing the sick today, just like He did 2,000 years ago.

00:02:25.467 --> 00:02:26.799
We just have to believe.

00:02:26.799 --> 00:02:35.189
I told you all the experience I had with the Lord at His crucifixion and Him talking to me about being healed.

00:02:35.539 --> 00:02:37.640
I believe with all my heart.

00:02:37.640 --> 00:02:41.000
I don't doubt in my heart about anything.

00:02:41.000 --> 00:02:46.879
I believe by faith that I call those things that be not as though they were.

00:02:47.159 --> 00:02:57.111
We call ourselves healed, whole, and well as we grow our faith and get in the Word more because we know the truth and the truth has set us free.

00:03:06.224 --> 00:03:06.688
It will be in every area of your life.

00:03:06.688 --> 00:03:16.140
If you have a foundation of the Word of God inside of you, no matter what your circumstance, it will change your circumstances.

00:03:17.090 --> 00:03:18.160
I believe that Jesus Christ is the healer.

00:03:21.093 --> 00:03:21.680
I believe it with all my heart in every area.

00:03:21.680 --> 00:03:25.474
No matter what, I'm not moved by what I see.

00:03:25.474 --> 00:03:28.914
As I'm overcoming this cough, I'm not moved by what I see.

00:03:44.860 --> 00:03:45.250
I'm not moved by what I feel: congestion.

00:04:00.870 --> 00:04:04.977
I'm not moved by what the devil tries to throw at me.

00:04:04.977 --> 00:04:07.420
I'm moved by what the Word says.

00:04:15.280 --> 00:04:16.103
It's foundation.

00:04:16.103 --> 00:04:23.510
He said in His Word, regardless of the cough, regardless of congestion or whatever, 'By His stripes, I am healed.

00:04:23.510 --> 00:04:25.840
' That is foundation, and that settles it.

00:04:25.840 --> 00:04:28.149
I'm not moved by what the circumstances say.

00:04:29.430 --> 00:04:34.490
If you're moved by what your flesh is telling you every single day, you're going to be moved by the circumstances.

00:04:34.490 --> 00:04:42.990
But you have to have your foot and your foundation planted on the Word of God and say, 'This flesh is not moving me.

00:04:55.371 --> 00:04:55.954
I see what the Bible says and I believe what the Bible says regardless of my circumstances.

00:04:55.954 --> 00:04:57.564
' It's foundation.

00:04:57.564 --> 00:05:01.063
That's why I tell you, you may be hurting financially.

00:05:01.063 --> 00:05:02.544
I take a financial seed.

00:05:05.919 --> 00:05:06.229
Every time we have a need, we sow a seed.

00:05:06.229 --> 00:05:09.911
People don't understand that, but I believe in seed faith.

00:05:21.004 --> 00:05:21.307
I believe if you have a need, just like a farmer, you go out and you plant the seed.

00:05:21.307 --> 00:05:23.120
That's what we do.

00:05:23.120 --> 00:05:31.410
We'll go out and say, 'Okay, well, we'll put a $100 here or whatever.

00:05:31.410 --> 00:05:40.000
' We sow that $100 and believe by faith that God's going to provide through supernatural income, that He'll give us an idea or He'll anoint us to do something.

00:05:40.000 --> 00:05:41.208
He'll give us favor.

00:05:42.072 --> 00:05:42.504
The Lord gives you favor.

00:05:42.504 --> 00:05:49.399
I believe a day of favor is worth more than a thousand days of working hard.

00:05:54.240 --> 00:05:59.390
All you need is a day of favor and the hand of the Lord moving favor in your life in every area if you just believe Him for it.

00:05:59.390 --> 00:06:05.582
But it takes you stepping out of the boat and walking on the water with Him for Him to come through.

00:06:10.080 --> 00:06:10.480
A lot of times it takes sacrificial things.

00:06:10.480 --> 00:06:12.675
He wants to see, 'How important am I to you?

00:06:12.675 --> 00:06:14.666
Do you have a hunger for me?

00:06:14.666 --> 00:06:16.160
Is it just lip service?

00:06:16.160 --> 00:06:22.879
' A lot of times we say a lot, but do we do what He asks us to do in His Word?

00:06:30.457 --> 00:06:30.651
Do we obey Him?

00:06:32.045 --> 00:06:32.297
Do we witness to our brother?

00:06:32.297 --> 00:06:33.668
Do we pray for him?

00:06:33.668 --> 00:06:37.250
Do we show the love of God to people when they're mean to us?

00:06:37.250 --> 00:06:42.760
Regardless of how they treat us, we're to operate in love.

00:06:42.760 --> 00:06:55.383
A lot of times that's not easy because our flesh gets all upset because we want to just say something bad back to them or do something stupid.

00:07:06.120 --> 00:07:13.060
You get off in the flesh and the devil gets a hold of you.

00:07:13.060 --> 00:07:19.919
That's where you have to stay in the law of love.

00:07:22.259 --> 00:07:24.582
Love takes no account of a suffered wrong.

00:07:24.582 --> 00:07:25.459
That's right.

00:07:36.520 --> 00:07:36.720
I have to practice it too.

00:07:36.720 --> 00:07:40.376
Every day I have to practice in the comment section.

00:07:40.376 --> 00:07:45.786
My son tells me somebody says something mean, and I say, 'Oh, we just love them.

00:07:45.786 --> 00:07:48.470
' We're not going to be moved by that.

00:07:48.470 --> 00:07:50.360
It's not them; they have a devil.

00:07:50.360 --> 00:07:54.391
They've got some kind of demonic spirit bothering them and that's why they retaliate the way they do.

00:07:54.391 --> 00:07:58.971
That's what you have to do.

00:07:58.971 --> 00:08:15.410
If somebody talks to you bad at work, at the store, or cuts you off driving down the road and you want to give them the California wave, you cannot allow yourself to yield over into the darkness.

00:08:18.599 --> 00:08:26.080
You have to say, 'Hey, I choose today to walk in love toward my wife, my children, and anybody who might try to tip my mood.

00:08:32.936 --> 00:08:33.279
I'm going to walk in love.

00:08:46.853 --> 00:08:47.147
I'm going to walk in love because faith works by love.

00:08:47.147 --> 00:08:56.850
If you're not walking in love and you don't see your faith producing something, if you don't see results in your faith every single day, you have to say, 'Where's my love walk?

00:08:56.850 --> 00:09:01.120
' because faith works by love because God is love.

00:09:01.120 --> 00:09:17.554
If you're not having faith move your mountain in your area for healing or demonstrations and manifestations of the glory—if you're not experiencing the fresh presence of the Lord every day in your life—you've got to check your love walk.

00:09:17.554 --> 00:09:20.468
How am I treating others around me?

00:09:20.468 --> 00:09:22.754
Because God is love, ladies and gentlemen.

00:09:29.966 --> 00:09:30.263
He dwells in us and we dwell in Him.

00:09:30.560 --> 00:09:35.040
He is in us, and I am seated with Him in the heavenlies.

00:09:39.724 --> 00:09:40.080
If you're in strife all the time, check your love walk.

00:09:40.080 --> 00:09:41.787
Check your love walk concerning your finances.

00:09:41.787 --> 00:09:43.067
Check your fear level.

00:09:43.067 --> 00:09:50.880
Check your sowing level, how you're giving and believing every day for what you're wanting the Lord to be a part of your finances.

00:09:50.880 --> 00:09:54.230
When you sow a seed, God will make you reap.

00:09:54.230 --> 00:10:00.293
For every seed you sow, I believe some thirty, sixty, or a hundred-fold.

00:10:04.697 --> 00:10:05.029
I believe that you can sow specifically for what you're believing for.

00:10:16.629 --> 00:10:16.1000
You say, 'Well, I'm believing for a new car.

00:10:16.1000 --> 00:10:22.107
' Well, where's your new car seed?

00:10:29.680 --> 00:10:29.910
So I sow for a new car to be paid for, or whatever.

00:10:42.669 --> 00:10:51.530
I take the seed of $100 and I say, 'I sow this seed, Father, in a direction toward what I'm believing for.

00:10:51.530 --> 00:10:56.480
' I'm believing, Father, for a creative idea to pay off the car.

00:10:56.480 --> 00:11:01.300
I'm believing for a creative idea, maybe I sow $10 for our electric bill.

00:11:01.300 --> 00:11:01.680
Whatever.

00:11:12.231 --> 00:11:12.453
You know what I'm saying?

00:11:18.616 --> 00:11:19.005
I'm just trying to help y'all.

00:11:19.394 --> 00:11:29.051
You take that seed and you believe for what you're sow towards, what you're believing for, and write the vision down.

00:11:29.051 --> 00:11:31.497
Take what you're believing for.

00:11:32.206 --> 00:11:37.359
I write down, 'Father, we're believing for a new house, a new car, for all these things, Father—new tires or whatever.

00:11:37.359 --> 00:11:39.829
' You know, God knows what you need.

00:11:39.829 --> 00:11:44.160
He said he shall supply all your needs according to his riches in glory by Christ Jesus.

00:11:44.160 --> 00:11:45.888
That's why I believe in the tithe.

00:11:45.888 --> 00:11:50.187
That's why I believe we have tither's rights.

00:11:50.187 --> 00:11:55.392
When you tithe, he said he rebukes the devourer for your sake.

00:11:55.392 --> 00:11:57.143
That's what the Lord said.

00:11:57.371 --> 00:12:00.773
And you say, 'Well, tithe is not for today.

00:12:00.773 --> 00:12:13.463
' But giving is, because he said, 'If you give, I'll give back to you: good measure, pressed down, shaken together, and running over shall men give into your bosom.

00:12:13.463 --> 00:12:16.992
' I believe that scripture is still in play.

00:12:27.639 --> 00:12:27.839
You say, 'Well, I don't believe in tithing.

00:12:27.839 --> 00:12:30.736
' I do.

00:12:45.347 --> 00:12:45.600
I believe in honoring the Father with my first fruits.

00:12:46.514 --> 00:12:48.286
You can't go wrong with trying to bless the Lord.

00:12:48.286 --> 00:12:53.104
Ladies and gentlemen, people try to get off on, 'Well, this is old covenant, new covenant.

00:12:53.104 --> 00:12:58.480
' I just say God knows my heart and he knows what I'm trying to do.

00:12:58.480 --> 00:13:01.744
He said every seed produces after its own kind.

00:13:08.575 --> 00:13:09.071
That's Bible.

00:13:09.071 --> 00:13:11.546
You'll reap what you sow.

00:13:14.640 --> 00:13:15.013
But it's not some thirty, some sixty.

00:13:15.013 --> 00:13:20.200
A farmer doesn't plant one seed in the ground to get one fruit back, one little corn back.

00:13:20.200 --> 00:13:22.000
He wants to get a bumper harvest.

00:13:22.000 --> 00:13:32.746
So, you've got to stretch your faith out there that God's going to anoint your mind to give you the ability to get what you need, whatever it may be.

00:13:32.746 --> 00:13:35.490
Because there are some of you really struggling.

00:13:37.271 --> 00:13:45.863
And I believe with all my heart, he'll give you a creative idea to do something in your life—a business, something good to put your hand to—so that you're not working for nothing.

00:13:45.863 --> 00:13:59.333
He doesn't want you working hard for nothing, being out there every single day struggling, working for minimum wage and going, 'Man, how are we going to make our bills today?

00:13:59.333 --> 00:14:04.217
' He's out there saying, 'I have cattle on a thousand hills.

00:14:04.217 --> 00:14:07.771
I have streets paved in gold.

00:14:07.771 --> 00:14:11.160
I've got a mansion for you when you come home.

00:14:11.160 --> 00:14:17.279
' You say, 'Well, I don't want any of that over here because it might ruin me.

00:14:17.279 --> 00:14:24.692
' You better work on your character then, because I'm telling you, God wants you to have exceedingly, abundantly above all that you dare ask or think.

00:14:24.692 --> 00:14:29.152
That scripture—not barely getting by, living in Lo-debar, busted and disgusted.

00:14:29.152 --> 00:14:34.949
'How am I going to make it every single day?

00:14:34.949 --> 00:14:40.137
' We have to buy the off-brand of everything because we can't even afford the good brand.

00:14:44.996 --> 00:14:45.218
And a lot of that is just like a couple of dollars more.

00:14:50.880 --> 00:14:51.120
And you think, 'Well, we can't do it.

00:14:51.120 --> 00:14:52.823
We've got to buy the off-brand.

00:14:52.823 --> 00:14:54.861
' Thank God we have the off-brand.

00:14:54.861 --> 00:15:01.484
But I'm saying God wants you to have exceedingly, abundantly above all that you dare ask or think, ladies and gentlemen.

00:15:01.484 --> 00:15:06.937
And I believe with all my heart, we're the King's kids, seated with him in the heavenlies.

00:15:06.937 --> 00:15:09.337
He doesn't want us living on food stamps.

00:15:09.337 --> 00:15:10.999
Thank God for food stamps.

00:15:10.999 --> 00:15:15.109
For some governments that have it, some people don't.

00:15:15.109 --> 00:15:15.931
Thank God.

00:15:15.931 --> 00:15:26.020
I lived on them for a long time, and I'm thankful for the government help they had because we needed it bad.

00:15:39.166 --> 00:15:39.509
But the Lord doesn't want you to live there is what I'm trying to say.

00:15:44.213 --> 00:15:44.480
And how do you get out of that?

00:15:44.480 --> 00:15:45.546
A dollar seed.

00:15:45.546 --> 00:15:50.800
If you have to just start with a dollar, a quarter, whatever.

00:15:51.806 --> 00:16:02.480
The Lord meets you where you're at and you sow to a ministry that's feeding you and you give to people that are feeding you spiritually.

00:16:10.630 --> 00:16:10.940
That's what I believe.

00:16:18.080 --> 00:16:18.320
And I'm telling you, if they're good ground—now, make sure they're good ground.

00:16:25.450 --> 00:16:25.600
If they're not good ground, do not give there.

00:16:35.657 --> 00:16:36.194
I'm just being real with y'all.

00:16:36.194 --> 00:16:41.199
I sowed to a lot of bad ground.

00:16:43.679 --> 00:16:43.919
And you go, 'Man, what is the deal?

00:16:43.919 --> 00:16:45.703
' And you keep sow there.

00:16:57.679 --> 00:16:58.319
What does it say?

00:17:07.645 --> 00:17:08.090
To keep doing the same thing expecting a different result is insanity.

00:17:08.090 --> 00:17:12.839
That's exactly what Christians do a lot of times.

00:17:12.839 --> 00:17:22.346
It sounds really harsh, but there's some ground—these people, they could be really corrupt in their ministry and you don't even know it.

00:17:22.346 --> 00:17:27.039
They're out doing bad things with the money and you're like, 'Man, I'm never getting anything back.

00:17:27.039 --> 00:17:38.507
' You've got to believe God for good ground and ask him, 'Lord, show me where to plant my seed that I reap back some thirty, some sixty, 100-fold.

00:17:38.507 --> 00:17:41.824
' I don't want to sow in bad ground.

00:17:46.880 --> 00:17:50.771
And I've told you all, I know there's ministries out there where the husbands will be cheating on their wives and everything.

00:17:58.070 --> 00:18:04.920
You don't know it for years and then all of a sudden you'll go, 'Well, that makes a lot of sense,' because the Lord will expose it finally.

00:18:04.920 --> 00:18:07.131
Follow your peace in your giving.

00:18:07.131 --> 00:18:11.199
Follow the peace that passes all understanding in your giving every day.

00:18:11.199 --> 00:18:16.302
Whenever you do something, no matter if it's just a quarter, follow your peace.

00:18:16.302 --> 00:18:21.337
And if you feel a check about something and you feel bothered about something, run!

00:18:21.337 --> 00:18:26.891
Because the Holy Spirit's trying to guide you into truth and to show you about them.

00:18:26.891 --> 00:18:37.725
If they teach you the word of God—if the pastor teaches you and your faith is getting fed and you're getting blessed spiritually—they're covering you spiritually—sow and help them.

00:18:51.920 --> 00:18:52.180
Your pastor that's taking care of you, they clean your nose, they pray for you when you're sick, they watch out for you.

00:18:52.180 --> 00:19:03.350
Seriously, they take care of your kids in the nursery and the nursery workers are back there feeding them goldfish.

00:19:03.360 --> 00:19:07.930
It takes money to do all that, ladies and gentlemen.

00:19:07.930 --> 00:19:17.990
You've got to bless the people that are helping you in your church, in your God, in your family.

00:19:23.013 --> 00:19:23.315
And if you don't like your church, find another one.

00:19:23.315 --> 00:19:27.170
Find a church that will teach you the word of God.

00:19:29.140 --> 00:19:30.190
You say, 'Well, I don't have one in my area.

00:19:30.190 --> 00:19:34.091
' Well, find something online on the weekdays to listen to.

00:19:34.091 --> 00:19:38.536
You've got to be feeding your spirit every day.

00:19:38.536 --> 00:19:42.180
You cannot go a day without feeding your spirit.

00:19:42.180 --> 00:19:56.179
If your flesh eats three times a day, you've got to find something to pour into your spirit throughout the day because we get weary in well-doing.

00:20:00.579 --> 00:20:00.909
You get tired.

00:20:00.909 --> 00:20:09.150
Your flesh gets in control and your spirit's over there going, 'Man, I'm starving and you haven't fed me in a week.

00:20:16.000 --> 00:20:16.640
You fed me last Sunday, but you haven't fed me since.

00:20:16.640 --> 00:20:25.139
' Your spirit man should be like Arnold Schwarzenegger, with big muscles, ready to kick the devil's butt.

00:20:25.139 --> 00:20:30.983
Because the devil comes to kill, steal, and destroy, ladies and gentlemen.

00:20:47.919 --> 00:20:48.229
And he's only able to kill, steal, and destroy the ones that are weak spiritually, lukewarm, weak spiritual babies.

00:20:48.229 --> 00:20:53.630
You've got to have that backbone like a crowbar that's able to say, 'No!

00:20:53.630 --> 00:20:57.726
When you come against me, sucker, you're going to get a fistful of knuckles!

00:20:57.726 --> 00:21:13.220
' I believe with all my heart that Jesus gave us the power and authority to tread on him, but you're not going to tread on him if you don't have a spiritual backbone.

00:21:14.120 --> 00:21:18.559
So, I don't know who that was for, but I'm supposed to pray.

00:21:18.559 --> 00:21:20.160
It just comes out.

00:21:20.160 --> 00:21:27.413
When you're full and you squeeze a sponge, it flows out regardless of what's in that sponge.

00:21:27.413 --> 00:21:28.231
It comes out.

00:21:28.231 --> 00:21:35.760
Bad stuff comes out of people when you touch them because out of the abundant overflow of the heart, the man speaks.

00:21:43.147 --> 00:21:43.493
And that's what happens when I get on these videos.

00:21:55.120 --> 00:21:55.326
I just start flowing.

00:21:55.326 --> 00:21:57.108
I say, "Okay, Lord, back to communion.

00:21:58.747 --> 00:22:00.880
" Father, I thank You for the body that was broken for us.

00:22:14.720 --> 00:22:15.627
I thank You, Father, that You died for us.

00:22:18.400 --> 00:22:20.250
We take this body in the name of Jesus.

00:22:20.250 --> 00:22:26.190
And I thank You, Lord, for my—that cough is gone.

00:22:26.190 --> 00:22:26.760
It's gone.

00:22:46.106 --> 00:22:46.453
And I thank You for Thieves.

00:23:05.867 --> 00:23:06.480
I thank You, Father, for all the things that You provide for us in this earth with oregano, garlic, and all the things that You provide for us, Father.

00:23:06.480 --> 00:23:08.320
Cayenne peppers and everything, Lord.

00:23:08.800 --> 00:23:12.667
You took it all and You made it for us.

00:23:12.667 --> 00:23:15.771
